author: desruisseaux
msg: Referencing: Rename NonLinearParameters as ContextualParameters since its purpose is not to describe the non-linear parameters
(this is done directly by the MathTransform implementation), but rather to put those non-linear parameters in their context.
Also start a refactoring as an implementation of ParameterValueGroup instead than a container for an other ParameterValueGroup.
This eliminate one level of indirection, which we hope will help to simplify a little bit the API.
